## Performance Targets

| Metric | MVP (Q3 2026) | v1.0 (Q1 2027) |
|---|---|---|
| Query latency P50 | < 300 ms | < 200 ms |
| Throughput | 5,000 QPS | 20,000 QPS |
| Index size | 1B documents | 10B documents |
| Crawl freshness | ≤ 60 min | ≤ 30 min |
| API uptime | 99.9% | 99.95% |

